@startuml
queue "RabbitMQ\n(Celery Broker)" as RabbitMQ
participant "Document Worker" as Worker
database "Document DB" as DocumentDB
participant "Cloudflare R2" as R2
participant "Cloudflare Workers AI" as LLM
database "Milvus\nVector Store" as Milvus

== Luồng nghiệp vụ: Xử lý tài liệu trong nền ==

RabbitMQ -> Worker: Consume process_document_task(doc_id)
activate Worker

Worker -> DocumentDB: Query Document by doc_id
activate DocumentDB
DocumentDB --> Worker: Document metadata
deactivate DocumentDB

Worker -> DocumentDB: UPDATE status=PROCESSING
activate DocumentDB
DocumentDB --> Worker: OK
deactivate DocumentDB

Worker -> R2: Download file gốc
activate R2
R2 --> Worker: Temp file
deactivate R2

Worker -> Worker: Trích xuất text và chunk tài liệu
Worker -> R2: Upload parsed content\n{user_id}/content/{doc_id}
activate R2
R2 --> Worker: OK
deactivate R2

Worker -> LLM: Tạo tóm tắt tài liệu
activate LLM
LLM --> Worker: Summary
deactivate LLM

Worker -> R2: Upload summary\n{user_id}/summary/{doc_id}
activate R2
R2 --> Worker: OK
deactivate R2

Worker -> Milvus: Upsert vector chunks\nmetadata={user_id, doc_id}
activate Milvus
Milvus --> Worker: OK
deactivate Milvus

Worker -> DocumentDB: UPDATE status=COMPLETED,\nhas_content=true, has_summary=true
activate DocumentDB
DocumentDB --> Worker: OK
deactivate DocumentDB

Worker --> RabbitMQ: Acknowledge task
deactivate Worker

alt Lỗi xử lý
    Worker -> DocumentDB: UPDATE status=FAILED, error_message
    Worker --> RabbitMQ: Retry hoặc reject theo cấu hình Celery
end

@enduml
